      <title>穆迪将太平洋投资管理公司支持的写字楼债务评级降至最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/moody-s-downgrades-debt-on-pimco-office-buildings-to-lowest-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于太平洋投资管理公司 (Pacific Investment Management Co.) 旗下一家办公室所支持的债券持续失去租户且利息支付缺口预期不断上升，穆迪评级公司 (Moody’s Ratings) 将此类债券的评级下调至最低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/moody-s-downgrades-debt-on-pimco-office-buildings-to-lowest-junk</guid>
